  "time_ut": 1658317272,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0da2\u0db1\u0dcf\u0db0\u0dd2\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0dad\u0dda\u0dbb\u0dd3\u0db8\u0dda\u0daf\u0dd3 \u0da2\u0db1\u0dad\u0dcf \u0db8\u0dad\u0dba\u0da7 \u0db4\u0dd2\u0da7\u0dd4\u0db4\u0dd1\u0dc0\u0dcf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "He turned his back on public opinion in the presidential election",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Dr. Omalpe Sobitha Thero, Chief Sanghanayake of Sri Lanka Ramanya Maha Nikaya, said that the people's opinion was not represented in the election of the President in the Parliament, and the MPs were not sensitive to the people's struggle.",
        "However, Sobitha Thero also stated that according to the demands made by religious leaders and civil organizations led by Maha Na Thero, the current administration should work to establish an all-party government very soon, to end the suffering of the people, to amend the constitution and to hold a general election as soon as possible.",
        "Sobitha Thero who said that the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna accused Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe of misleading the country in 2019, and said that Mr. Wickramasinghe was also deprived of his parliamentary seat by saying that he was a thief, a traitor and a person who sold out the country who committed the bond fraud.",
        "Omalpe Sobitha Thero said that if Mr. Ranil Wickremesinghe rejects the allegations, action should be taken against those who made false accusations against him. He also said that he questions whether Mr. Dinesh Gunawardena has the legal and moral right to propose Mr. Ranil Wickremesinghe as a thief for the post of President. .",
        "He also said that the people are waiting to send home those who stole, cheated and told lies in the next election."
      ],
